---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <div class="px-4 py-20">
    <section
      class="py-40 flex p-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto gap-20 items-center bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-600 to-indigo-950 text-white"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
        <h1 class="font-semibold text-4xl md:text-6xl">
          Learn to Code Golf in TypeScript's Type System
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl">
          Master the type system in 6-8 weeks <br />
           (or, get pretty good in 10-30 minutes)
        </p>
      </div>
      <img src="/tsgolf/typescript.svg" class="w-1/3 hidden md:block" />
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-bold">Get Started!</h2>
    <div class="flex gap-5 py-10">
      <div class="p-8 border basis-1/3 flex flex-col gap-2">
        <p class="font-semibold">Start the Tour</p>
        <p>
          TSGolf's
          <a href="/tsgolf/tour" class="text-sky-800 underline">tour</a>
           is a great way to start your journey with TypeScript's type system.
          We have many detailed examples and tips on this site, and the tour
          will guide you through the most important lessons as you learn more
          and more concepts and put your knowledge into practice with
          challenges.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-8 border basis-1/3 flex flex-col gap-2">
        <p class="font-semibold">Join the chatroom</p>
        <p>
          We have a <a
            href="https://chat.stackexchange.com/rooms/145771/typescript-type-system"
            >nice chatroom</a
          > for discussion of code-golfing in TypeScript's type system over on <a
            class="text-sky-700 underline"
            href="https://codegolf.stackexchange.com"
            >Code Golf Stack Exchange</a
          >.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-600">
          <b>Note:</b> You must have 20 reputation on any Stack Exchange site
          (such as Stack Overflow) before the site will let you chat.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-8 border basis-1/3 flex flex-col gap-2">
        <p class="font-semibold">Start golfing!</p>
        <p>
          We have quite a lot of <a
            href="/tsgolf/challenges"
            class="text-sky-800 underline">challenges</a
          > here with leaderboards <span class="text-orange-800">
            (Not yet implemented)
          </span> to get you started! If you want to move on to potentially
          harder and/or more interesting challenges, <a
            class="text-sky-700 underline"
            href="https://codegolf.stackexchange.com"
            >Code Golf Stack Exchange</a
          > is a great place to compete in TypeScript's type system.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

